snippet.title: SHIVA SHIVA | Lyrical | Kannada | KD | KVN Production | Prem's | AJ | Dhruva Sarja |Reeshma| Suprith
snippet.description:
Presenting Shiva Shiva Lyrical Song From The Movie KD-The Devil  Starring: Dhruva Sarja, Reeshma Nanaiah, Shilpa Shetty & Others Exclusive Only On Anand Audio Official Youtube Channel..!!! 
----------------------------------------------
#KD #KDTHEDEVIL  #KVNProductions #shivashiva  #prems  #jogiprem #kdfirstsingle #kdsong #arjunjanya #kailashkher  #shilpashetty  #ramesharavind #vravichandran  #reeshmananaiah #dhruvasarja  #manjugowdabs  #showmanprem #youtube #anandaudio
----------------------------------------------
Song : Shiva Shiva Lyrical Song
Singers : Prem's, Kailash Kher
Lyricist : Manjunath BS
----------------------------------------------
To Listen On Your Favourite Music Streaming Platform
♪ Spotify : https://tinyurl.com/yc5wcnuv
♪ Jiosaavn : https://tinyurl.com/2cd9efn6

----------------------------------------------
ಪಲ್ಲವಿ :
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ ಶಿವ
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಚರಣ 1:
ಹತ್ತೂರಿನ ಒಡೆಯ ನೀನು, ಗೊತ್ತೇನೋ ಯಾರು ನಿಂಗೆ...
ಸೈನ್ಯಾನೆ ಇಲ್ಲ ಇವನ್ಗೆ, ಹೊಂಟವ್ನೆ ರಾಜ ನಂಗೆ..
ಬೆಳಗಾಗೋದ್ರಲ್ಲೇ ಬೆಳೆದಾ...ಬೆಳಗಾಗೋದ್ರಲ್ಲೇ ಬೆಳೆದು ಫೇಮಸ್ಸು ಆಗೋದ್ನಲ್ಲ..
ನಾನು ನಾನ್ ಅಂದೋರ್ಗೆಲ್ಲಾ ತೊಡೆತಟ್ಟಿ ನಿಂತವ್ನ್ ನೋಡ್ಲಾ..
ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ನೋಡೋ..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಚರಣ 2:
ದೌಲತ್ತಲ್ ಮೆರದೋರೆಲ್ಲ ಹಿಸ್ಟರಿ ಲಿ ಉಳಿದೆಯಿಲ್ಲ..
ಕಾಲೇಳೆಯೋಕ್ ಬಂದೋರೆಲ್ಲ ಕಾಲ ಕೆಳ್ಗೆ ಉಳ್ದೊದ್ರಲ್ಲ
ನೀನ್ ಅಂತೋನ್ ಅಲ್ವೇ ಅಲ್ಲ...ನೀನ್ ಅಂತೋನ್ ಅಲ್ವೇ ಅಲ್ಲ... ನಿನ್ನಂಗೆ ಯಾರು ಇಲ್ಲ..
ಬಕೇಟಾ ಹಿಡಿಯೋರ್ನೆಲ್ಲ ಸೈಡಿಟ್ಟು ಹೋಯ್ತಯೀರ್ಲಾ ..
ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ಬೆಳೆದ ನೋಡೋ..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್..
ಗುರುವೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ..
ಶಿವನೇ ನಿನ್ನಾಟ ಬಲ್ಲೋರ್ ಯಾರ್ ಯಾರೋ, ಶಿವಾ..
ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..ಶಿವಾ..

snippet.title: पंकजा मुंडे, धनंजय मुंडे यांच्यासोबत फोटो, कमरेला बंदूक लावणारे परळीतला Nikhil Kailas Phad कोण आहे?
snippet.description:
#NikhilPhad #KailasPhad #Gun #KailasPhad #SantoshDeshmukh #Beed #Parli #PankajaMunde #DhananjayMunde #WalmikKarad  

बीडच्या मस्साजोग मध्ये घडलेल्या सरपंच संतोष देशमुख यांच्या खूनानं महाराष्ट्र हादरुन निघाला आहे. या घटनेमुळे बीडमधील कायदा सुव्यवस्थेचे तीन तेरा वाजलेले असल्याचं दिसून येतंय. भाजप आमदार सुरेश धस, आमदार संदीप क्षीरसागर यांनी या प्रकरणावरुन मंत्री धनंजय मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांना लक्ष केलं जातंय. आवादा वाईन्ड मिलच्या खंडणीचा प्रकरणात मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांवर खंडणीचा गुन्हा दाखल झालेला आहे. यावरुन मंत्री असलेल्या धनंजय मुंडेंवर सरकारमधील आमदारांसह विरोधीपक्ष त्यांना मंत्रिपदापासून दूर ठेवा मागणी करत होता. पण आता त्यांना पालकमंत्रीपदापासून दूर ठेवा असा सूर दिसत आहे. अशातच सामाजिक कार्यकर्त्या अंजली दमानियांनी कायदा सुव्यवस्थेवरुन सवाल उपस्थित केले आहेत.

इंडिया टुडेच्या मुंबई तक या मराठी युट्यूब चॅनलवर आपलं स्वागत. इंडिया टुडे ग्रुपचे मॅगझिन, इंडिया टुडे टीव्ही आणि आज तक हे लोकप्रिय न्यूज चॅनल आपल्याला माहितीच आहे. त्यानंतर आता खास मराठी प्रेक्षकांसाठी आपण भारतीय प्रादेशिक भाषेतलं पहिलं मराठी चॅनल घेऊन आलोय. महाराष्ट्रासह राष्ट्रीय आणि आंतरराष्ट्रीयस्तरावरील महत्वाच्या बातम्या आणि घडामोडी आपल्याला अगदी सोप्या शब्दांत समजावण्याचा आमचा प्रयत्न असणार आहे.

mr.description:
#NikhilPhad #KailasPhad #Gun #KailasPhad #SantoshDeshmukh #Beed #Parli #PankajaMunde #DhananjayMunde #WalmikKarad  

बीडच्या मस्साजोग मध्ये घडलेल्या सरपंच संतोष देशमुख यांच्या खूनानं महाराष्ट्र हादरुन निघाला आहे. या घटनेमुळे बीडमधील कायदा सुव्यवस्थेचे तीन तेरा वाजलेले असल्याचं दिसून येतंय. भाजप आमदार सुरेश धस, आमदार संदीप क्षीरसागर यांनी या प्रकरणावरुन मंत्री धनंजय मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांना लक्ष केलं जातंय. आवादा वाईन्ड मिलच्या खंडणीचा प्रकरणात मुंडेंचे निकटवर्तीय वाल्मिक कराडांवर खंडणीचा गुन्हा दाखल झालेला आहे. यावरुन मंत्री असलेल्या धनंजय मुंडेंवर सरकारमधील आमदारांसह विरोधीपक्ष त्यांना मंत्रिपदापासून दूर ठेवा मागणी करत होता. पण आता त्यांना पालकमंत्रीपदापासून दूर ठेवा असा सूर दिसत आहे. अशातच सामाजिक कार्यकर्त्या अंजली दमानियांनी कायदा सुव्यवस्थेवरुन सवाल उपस्थित केले आहेत.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

snippet.title: Bhide ने डाला Dr. Hathi पे बाल्टी भर पानी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | New Year Countdown
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Bhide is out in his living room, relaxing as he reads the newspaper. But soon his peace gets disrupted by Tapu Sena's constant noise and he tells them to keep quiet! Find out more by watching the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #newyearcountdown #newyear2025 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch more clips from New Year Countdown: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G2wI91egSQvmRpJMIXBOmIa

overthink himsaku just say dhop

snippet.description: We prepare Orange Jam Marmalade in the peaceful landscapes of our village, blending fresh oranges, sugar, and traditional cooking methods in an open-air setting. Surrounded by lush greenery and nature’s beauty, we create a sweet and tangy marmalade, perfect for spreading on fresh bread, pairing with snacks, or enhancing desserts. The natural environment adds to the charm, showcasing the simplicity and joy of village-style cooking.

snippet.title: പാട്ടും പ്രണയവും പങ്ക് വെച്ച് ക്രിസും ദിവ്യയും |  ASWAMEDHAM -53 | kris venugopal and divya sreedhar
snippet.description:
പാട്ടും പ്രണയവും പങ്ക് വെച്ച് ക്രിസും ദിവ്യയും |  ASWAMEDHAM -53 | kris venugopal and divya sreedhar 

ടെലിവിഷൻ ചരിത്രത്തിൽ ആദ്യമായി സംപ്രേഷണം ചെയ്യപ്പെട്ട റിവേഴ്‌സ് ക്വിസ് 
ഫോർമാറ്റിൽ ഉള്ള ഒരു  ഇൻറ്റലകച്വൽ ഗെയിം ഷോ ആണ് അശ്വമേധം. 2001 ഇൽ കൈരളി ചാനലിൽ സംപ്രേഷണം ചെയ്തു തുടങ്ങിയ അശ്വമേധം എന്ന ആശയത്തിൻ്റെ സ്രഷ്ടാവും, പരിപാടിയുടെ അവതാരകനായ ഗ്രാൻഡ്മാസ്റ്ററും  തിരുവനന്തപുരം സ്വദേശിയായ ഡോ. ജി എസ്‌ പ്രദീപ് ആണ്. 
#rahuleaswar #gspradeep #kairalitv 
ഗെയിമിൽ പങ്കെടുക്കുന്ന വ്യക്തി/മത്സരാർത്ഥി മനസ്സിൽ ഓർമ്മിക്കുന്ന ഒരാളെ 21 യെസ് ഓർ നോ ചോദ്യങ്ങളുടെ ഉത്തരങ്ങളിലൂടെ കണ്ടെത്തുക എന്ന ദൗത്യമാണ് ഗ്രാൻഡ്മാസ്റ്റർ അഥവാ ഷോ മാസ്റ്ററുടേത്. ഗ്രാൻഡ്മാസ്റ്ററുടെ ചോദ്യങ്ങൾക്ക് അതേ/അല്ല എന്ന ഉത്തരങ്ങൾ ആവും മത്സരാർത്ഥി നൽകുക. ഗ്രാൻഡ്മാസ്റ്ററുടെ ഏതെങ്കിലും ചോദ്യം മനസ്സിലാവാതെ വരികയോ.., മത്സരാർത്ഥിക്ക് മനസ്സിൽ വിചാരിച്ച വ്യക്തിയെക്കുറിച്ചുള്ള കൃത്യമായ സൂചനകൾ ഓർത്തെടുക്കാൻ പറ്റാതെ വരികയോ ചെയ്‌താൽ മത്സരാർത്ഥി ജൂറിയുടെ സഹായം തേടി ഗെയിമിൽ മുന്നേറുന്നു. ആദ്യത്തെ പത്തു ചോദ്യങ്ങൾ ഉൾപ്പെടുന്ന റൌണ്ട് 'യാഗം' എന്നും പിന്നീടുള്ള അഞ്ചു ചോദ്യങ്ങൾ ഉൾപ്പെടുന്ന റൌണ്ട് 'യജ്ഞം' എന്നും തുടർന്നുള്ള ചോദ്യങ്ങൾ ഉൾപ്പെടുന്ന റൌണ്ട് 'രാജസൂയം'  എന്നും അറിയപ്പെടുന്നു.

Ashwamedham is an intellectual game show, first aired in 2001 on Kairali TV in a reverse quiz format, making it a pioneering concept in the history of television. Dr. G.S. Pradeep, a native of Thiruvananthapuram, "the Grandmaster" is both the creator of the concept and the host of the show.
The role of the Grandmaster is to identify the personality the contestant has in mind by asking up to 21 yes-or-no questions. Each contestant responds with either "Yes" or "No" to the Grandmaster's inquiries. If the Grandmaster struggles to interpret the answers or if the contestant cannot recall specific clues, the Jury may assist. The rounds are structured as follows: the first 10 questions form the 'Yagam' round, the next 5 make up the 'Yajnam' round, and the final set is the 'Rajasuyam' round.

ഗെയിമിൽ പങ്കെടുക്കുന്ന വ്യക്തി/മത്സരാർത്ഥി മനസ്സിൽ ഓർമ്മിക്കുന്ന ഒരാളെ 21 യെസ് ഓർ നോ ചോദ്യങ്ങളുടെ ഉത്തരങ്ങളിലൂടെ കണ്ടെത്തുക എന്ന ദൗത്യമാണ് ഗ്രാൻഡ്മാസ്റ്റർ അഥവാ ഷോ മാസ്റ്ററുടേത്. ഗ്രാൻഡ്മാസ്റ്ററുടെ ചോദ്യങ്ങൾക്ക് അതേ/അല്ല എന്ന ഉത്തരങ്ങൾ ആവും മത്സരാർത്ഥി നൽകുക. ഗ്രാൻഡ്മാസ്റ്ററുടെ ഏതെങ്കിലും ചോദ്യം മനസ്സിലാവാതെ വരികയോ.., മത്സരാർത്ഥിക്ക് മനസ്സിൽ വിചാരിച്ച വ്യക്തിയെക്കുറിച്ചുള്ള കൃത്യമായ സൂചനകൾ ഓർത്തെടുക്കാൻ പറ്റാതെ വരികയോ ചെയ്‌താൽ മത്സരാർത്ഥി ജൂറിയുടെ സഹായം തേടി ഗെയിമിൽ മുന്നേറുന്നു. ആദ്യത്തെ പത്തു ചോദ്യങ്ങൾ ഉൾപ്പെടുന്ന റൌണ്ട് 'യാഗം' എന്നും പിന്നീടുള്ള അഞ്ചു ചോദ്യങ്ങൾ ഉൾപ്പെടുന്ന റൌണ്ട് 'യജ്ഞം' എന്നും തുടർന്നുള്ള ചോദ്യങ്ങൾ ഉൾപ്പെടുന്ന റൌണ്ട് 'രാജസൂയം'  എന്നും അറിയപ്പെടുന്നു.

Ashwamedham is an intellectual game show, first aired in 2001 on Kairali TV in a reverse quiz format, making it a pioneering concept in the history of television. Dr. G.S. Pradeep, a native of Thiruvananthapuram, "the Grandmaster" is both the creator of the concept and the host of the show.
The role of the Grandmaster is to identify the personality the contestant has in mind by asking up to 21 yes-or-no questions. Each contestant responds with either "Yes" or "No" to the Grandmaster's inquiries. If the Grandmaster struggles to interpret the answers or if the contestant cannot recall specific clues, the Jury may assist. The rounds are structured as follows: the first 10 questions form the 'Yagam' round, the next 5 make up the 'Yajnam' round, and the final set is the 'Rajasuyam' round.

During a critical rescue operation, Abhijeet tragically loses his daughter Shreya due to a minor error by Daya. Three months later, a mysterious shooting incident occurs on a metro, leaving a woman injured. How will ACP Pradyuman and his team uncover the truth behind this case?

snippet.title: LIVE BOOK LAUNCH | 482nd BOOK BY A.RATNASUNDERSURISHWARJI M.S.| 24th Dec | LIVE from BalsanaTirth
snippet.description:
Gurudev is a motivator, spiritual guru, an author, lecturer and a teacher of life. 
Aacharya Ratnasundersurishwarji Maharaj Saheb
Raj Pratibodhak Sarasvati Nandan Param Poojya Acharya Vijay Ratnasundersuriswarji is a renowned Jain saint. He was born on 5th January, 1948 at Depla (Near Palitana, Gujarat).
Being a religious guru, he wrote many visionary books for the sociol and cultural upliftment of the individual as well as society.

*Lakhi rakho aaras ni takti par*
 *Jher jyare nitri jai che*  these are the few of books which have brought about a sea change in the lives of many, across the globe.
He has written more than 450 books in gujarati.
Which are also been translated in English, Hindi, Marathi, Urdu, French in the hope of bringing positive change in all the people.

Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

Aajya teri nazar utaru uljhi ye zulaf swaru
Ambran te aai apsara tere pe jaan bhi vaaru
Nadiyan or jheel ye jharne sab terte baat kare
Palke teri uthe swera jhukjya te raat kare
Sheeshe pe matna puche dekhle meri ankhya mein
Ladyu tere kan ke niche madam tikka kala main
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

Deewana main tera tu meri mehbuba
Dhundhe ye meri nigahe tujhko hawao mein
Main toh kuch na mangu tu jo hasil hai
Haan bas marna chahu main toh teri bahon mein
Khulya tane asman dyu khushiyan ki chhatri taan dyu
Sapne tere pure kardyu na rakhu kade talya main
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

Duniya tane sari dekhe
Tu meri taraf lkha
Chandan ki lakad hai tu bangya main sarp mkha
Aave har saal december chede ya dhund maney
Tha tha ke patke madam jaddya ki boond maney
Bille pe hath hai uska aadi na ant hai jiska
Mannat je puri hogi ladyu dive aalya main
Ankhiya mein khogya chora
Khogya tere baalan mein
Bhavre bhi pagal tere
Ittar ki khushbu gaalan mein

📝 𝐋𝐲𝐫𝐢𝐜𝐬: Gujarati 👇 

હે હે હે ફેસબુક માં ફોટો તારો વર્ષો જૂનો જોયો રે હો હો હો... (૨)
ઢેગલડી મારી આઈ મને બાળપણ ની યાદો રે
હે હે હે દાડા વિત્યા મહિના વિત્યા વિતી ગયા વર્ષો રે હો હો હો
મોનીતી મારી તાજી થઈ ગઈ બધી યાદો રે હે હે હે
ઢેગલડી મારી આઈ મને બાળપણ ની યાદો રે...

હો નોના નોના હતા આપણે ઢેગલ ભેળા રમતા
લાડો લાડો થઈ ને એક બીજા ને પરણતા
હો હો હો તારા મારા લગ્ન ના ગોણા મધરા ગાતા
ધૂળ નો ઢગલો કરીને ફેરા આપણ ફરતા
હે હે હે નોનપણ નો નેડો આજ સાને ભુલી બેઠા રે હો હો હો
રૂપલડી મારી રૂબરુ મળવાને મન તરસે રે
હે હે હે ફેસબુક માં ફોટો તારો વર્ષો જૂનો જોયો રે હો હો હો
ઢેગલડી મારી આઈ મને બાળપણ ની યાદો રે... (૨)

હો કેમ થયા જુદા આપણ નથી અમે જાણતા
મળ્યાં એવા મેસજ તમે મોહાળ માં જઈ ભણતા
હો હો હો હસો મજા માં એટલે અમને યાદ નથી કર્તા
યાદ કરી ને ગામડે તમે આટો નથી મારતા

snippet.title: Subedaar – First Look | Anil Kapoor | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
A special day calls for a special announcement 🎂 
#Subedaar, new movie, coming soon

ABOUT SUBEDAAR
Set in the Indian heartland, the powerful masala action-drama follows Subedaar Arjun Maurya as he grapples with the challenges of leading a civilian life, navigates a strained relationship with his daughter and confronts societal dysfunction. Once a soldier who fought for the nation,
Subedaar must now battle enemies within to protect his home and family.

Directed by: Suresh Triveni
Produced by: Vikram Malhotra, Anil Kapoor, Suresh Triveni
Written by: Suresh Triveni, Prajwal Chandrashekar
An Opening Image Films and Anil Kapoor Film & Communication Network (AKFCN) Production

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: Live Meditation With Gurudev | World Meditation Day 21st Dec 2024
snippet.description:
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 on the occasion of World Meditation Day to meditate with Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar, this is going to be the most historic and largest meditation event. You don't want to miss out!

About #Gurudev - 
The world is coming together on the 21st of December 2024 to celebrate World Meditation Day 
World-renowned humanitarian, spiritual leader, and an ambassador of peace and human values. Through his life and work, Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar has inspired millions around the world with a vision of a stress-free and peaceful world. Gurudev founded The Art of Living, a non-profit organization that is engaged in stress-management and service initiatives across the world.

snippet.title: Baba Ramdev Invites Kamiya Jani To Spend A Day With Him | Stories From Bharat Ep 47 | Curly Tales
snippet.description:
In this episode of Stories From Bharat, we uncover the fascinating journey of the Patanjali Group of Companies, founded by the dynamic duo Swami Ramdev and Acharya Balakrishna. With a valuation close to ₹1,00,000 crore and directly and indirectly employing over 5 lakh Indians, Patanjali has become a cornerstone of the India growth story, combining business, wellness, and culture.

Join me as I explore the universe Baba Ramdev has created in Haridwar, from the Patanjali Yogpeeth to the Wellness Centre, Gurukul, and University. Is Baba Ramdev a spiritual guru or a strategic businessman? Find out as we delve into his mission to stay true to Indian roots while building a global empire.

I also had the rare privilege of spending a day with Acharya Balakrishna, the co-founder of Patanjali. From running at 4:30 AM to yoga sessions, cycling live on Facebook, and sharing a meal, this episode reveals how he manages to inspire and lead at 60 while contributing significantly to India’s economy.

Watch now to discover how Patanjali is shaping wellness, empowering people, and redefining the global perception of Indian heritage.

#StoriesFromBharat #BabaRamdev #Patanjali #Yoga #IndiaGrowthStory #AcharyaBalakrishna #makeinindia

Sonu and Tapu find themselves in a panic when their families start looking for compatible life partners. Will they have the ability to devise a strategy, desperate to dodge arranged marriages?

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

#immunitybooster #halwa 

3 चीज़ो से ये ताकतवर पेंद बनाके खालो घुटना-कमर,जोड़ों का दर्द कभी नहीं होगा calcium भरपूर मिलेगा |PEND recipe

Calcium se bharpur Til God aur Makhana ki yah pend aapko Apne diet Mein Jarur Shamil Karni chahie yah sardiyon ki bahut hi acchi recipe hai jhuthi bina kaju badam ke Bankar taiyar Hogi aur bahut hi jyada healthy Rahegi strong bonds ke liye sharp mind ke liye vitamin ki deficiency ko Dur karne ke liye bahut hi jyada acchi remedy hai to jarur try kare

If you want to stay healthy then you don't have to change your lifestyle just include this healthy recipe in your diet........
Meri recipe Banane mein bahut Aasan hai aap ise Ghar per maujud Saman Se Aaram Se banaa sakte hain
रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

*INGREDIENTS required :-

3 cup - Lotus Seeds
1/2cup - Sesame Seeds
1/4cup - Edible Gum
2 cup - Milk
3/4cup - Jaggery
1ts - Peppermul Powder
1ts - White Pepper Powder
1/2ts - Ginger Powder
1/2ts - Green Cardamom Powder
2 pinch - Nutmeg
3-4tbs - Clarified Butter

रेसिपी देखने के बाद एक बार घर पर इसे ट्राई जरूर करिएगा अगर पसंद आए तो कमेंट करके जरूर बताइएगा क्या आपकी पूरी फैमिली मेंबर्स का क्या रिएक्शन रहा मुझे उम्मीद है कि सब के सब इसे जरूर पसंद करेंगे

snippet.title: Best School in the World | School Aaj Kal | Take A Break
snippet.description:
What would schools say if they dropped the facade and got real? Welcome to School Aaj Kal, a hilarious yet thought-provoking comedy sketch that imagines just that! 🎓💸
In this video, we explore how schools today often focus more on profits than education, becoming money-churning machines rather than true centers of learning. From exorbitant fees and "mandatory" extracurriculars to endless add-ons like "smart classrooms" and overpriced uniforms, this sketch dives into the absurdities of modern-day schooling with a pinch of satire and a truckload of laughs.

Get ready to laugh, relate, and maybe even question the reality of today’s education system. Because sometimes, honesty is the funniest policy! 😂
#SchoolAajKal #HonestSchools #EducationSatire

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Producer - Pratik Thakur
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4275 - Sonu ne Kyu Thukrayi Rishte ki Baat! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor.
